cs.DB, cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CR

This paper deals with the problem of query pricing for selling access to data, which is a topic closely related to databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the notion of arbitrage-freeness, which is a concept from game theory (cs.GT). The formulation of the problem as a revenue maximization problem with single-minded buyers and unlimited supply suggests that it could also be categorized under algorithms and complexity (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), or cryptography and security (cs.CR).
